description:
Creative and educational games for children that help your child spend time with an electronic device effectively. Let your child feel like a real artist! The app includes coloring activities that are friendly to the youngest children, as well as drawing lessons designed to develop fine motor skills. Additionally, the app contains pictures on different topics that will entertain your child with fascinating sounds and funny characters. Here's what awaits you:

-11 thematic packs with 165 pages;
-Easy coloring for children;
-Drawing lessons;
-Creativity development.

The app is designed for children of preschool age and is also suitable for boys and girls aged 2-4 years. All activities were developed with the participation of experts in the field of children's education and include educational elements such as developing fine motor skills and logic. 

Have fun!
